{"cursor":"5491","size":15,"audio":[],"currentlang":"en","article":"{{Multiple issues|\n\n\n\n\n}}\n\n\n'Now and Later' is a brand of fruit-flavored taffy-like product manufactured by\nFerrara Candy Company. The candy is organized into squares packaged in colorful\npaper. The original Now and Later colors were red, green and blue. Throughout\nits lifetime, Now and Later has developed many unique flavors (see list below).\nTwelve flavors are currently available. http://www.ferrarausa.com/now-later-fun-\nfacts/\n\n\"Hard 'N Fruity Now and Soft 'N Chewy Later,\" the slogan found on each square's\nwrapping, replaces \"Eat Some Now. Save Some for Later.\"\n","linknr":152,"url":"Now_and_Later","recorded":1362540322,"links":20,"instances":["candy"],"pdf":[],"categories":["Brand name confectionery"],"headings":["History","Now and Later flavors","References","External links"],"image":["//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/f/f4/Ambox_content.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/a/a4/Text_document_with_red_question_mark.svg/40px-Text_document_with_red_question_mark.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/99/Question_book-new.svg/50px-Question_book-new.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/f/f2/Edit-clear.svg/40px-Edit-clear.svg.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/2c/Now-and-Later-Wrapper-Small.jpg/300px-Now-and-Later-Wrapper-Small.jpg","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b2/Now-and-Laters.jpg/290px-Now-and-Laters.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/08/Wiki_Now_and_Later_with_product.jpg/250px-Wiki_Now_and_Later_with_product.jpg","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png","//bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf10/skins/vector/images/search-ltr.png?303-4","//bits.wikimedia.org/images/wikim